      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW KARSON (1) was impressive last start despite finishing second, recording an enormous 22.05 to place behind Aston Pastizzi and clocking a new PB this course and distance. Expected to go close if runs up to latest. NALA'S GHOST (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (24.51) at Bendigo. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from 10 starts. Great chance to atone. PAW JUDD (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (22.61) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Cannot be underestimated. PAW PASCAL (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
